>cleveref – Intelligent cross-referencing&lt;/a>&lt;/li>
&lt;/ol></description></item><item><title>Docker 搭建 ShareLaTeX</title><link>https://jinggqu.github.io/posts/docker-host-sharelatex/</link><pubDate>Thu, 11 Mar 2021 08:00:00 +0800</pubDate><guid>https://jinggqu.github.io/posts/docker-host-sharelatex/</guid><description>&lt;h1 id="docker-搭建-sharelatex">Docker 搭建 ShareLaTeX
&lt;/h1>&lt;h2 id="安装-sharelatex">安装 ShareLaTeX
&lt;/h2>&lt;div class="highlight">&lt;div class="chroma">
&lt;table class="lntable">&lt;tr>&lt;td class="lntd">
&lt;pre tabindex="0" class="chroma">&lt;code>&lt;span class="lnt">1
&lt;/span>&lt;span class="lnt">2
&lt;/span>&lt;/code>&lt;/pre>&lt;/td>
&lt;td class="lntd">
&lt;pre tabindex="0" class="chroma">&lt;code class="language-bash" data-lang="bash">&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">sudo su
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">docker pull kingsleyluoxin/sharelatex:full
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;/code>&lt;/pre>&lt;/td>&lt;/tr>&lt;/table>
&lt;/div>
&lt;/div>&lt;h2 id="编辑配置">编辑配置
&lt;/h2>&lt;p>在 &lt;code>~/sharelatex&lt;/code> 中放入配置文件 &lt;code>docker-compose.yml&lt;/code>，并进行编辑。&lt;/p>
&lt;div class="highlight">&lt;div class="chroma">
&lt;table class="lntable">&lt;tr>&lt;td class="lntd">
&lt;pre tabindex="0" class="chroma">&lt;code>&lt;span class="lnt">1
&lt;/span>&lt;span class="lnt">2
&lt;/span>&lt;/code>&lt;/pre>&lt;/td>
&lt;td class="lntd">
&lt;pre tabindex="0" class="chroma">&lt;code class="language-bash" data-lang="bash">&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">&lt;span class="nb">cd&lt;/span> ~/sharelatex
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">vim docker-compose.yml
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;/code>&lt;/pre>&lt;/td>&lt;/tr>&lt;/table>
